/* ==UserStyle==
@name           Inoreader NO ADS - new card view
@namespace      USO Archive
@author         Eugene Veprytskyi
@description    `Inoreader new Big card view with 4 tiles on any screen resolution. No ADS at all.IMPORTANT DON`T USE ADBLOCK, ADS will be removed by css styles!!!changelog:fixed padding in list viewfixed issue with list and other type of view`
@version        20200402.10.43
